Tang San pasti sedih.

537
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:21,060
Jangan membentaknya.

538
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:22,940
Aku bantu kau cari lagi.

539
00:32:25,610 --> 00:32:26,020
Ou Sike.

540
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:27,970
Berikan Kiwi Mempercepat Terbang.

541
00:32:31,090 --> 00:32:32,820
Bukankah kau bilang
jika ke sana akan mati?

542
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:33,420
Aku tahu.

543
00:32:33,420 --> 00:32:34,570
Kau pergi juga akan mati.

544
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:36,370
-Karena itu, kalian jangan pergi.
