545
00:32:36,370 --> 00:32:37,650
Aku berjanji mau menemaninya.

546
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:38,660
Bantu aku.

547
00:32:41,450 --> 00:32:43,370
Kiwi Mempercepat Terbang!

548
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:46,420
Tang San!

549
00:32:52,140 --> 00:32:52,810
Kepala Akademi.

550
00:32:54,090 --> 00:32:54,540
